(
<figureCitation box="[537,608,835,861]" captionStart="FIGURE 7" captionStartId="5.[151,250,1339,1363]" captionTargetBox="[161,1421,965,1315]" captionTargetId="figure-297@5.[151,1436,957,1315]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 7. Holotype of Robinsonia decaensi Laguerrre sp. nov., dorsal view on the left and ventral view on the right, labels are not to scale. Scale 10 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4982848" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4982848/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="70">Fig. 7</figureCitation>
). 
<emphasis box="[633,828,835,861]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="70">Head and thorax</emphasis>
. Antennae bipectinate, shaft and rami greyish beige, scape light ochreous. Frons mixed with white and brownish grey, vertex yellowish with white base. Patagia, tegulae and thorax, white. Palpi light brownish grey, last segment very short.
</paragraph>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4982848" ID-Zenodo-Dep="4982848" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4982848/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="70" startId="5.[151,250,1339,1363]" targetBox="[161,1421,965,1315]" targetPageId="5">
